-
-### 1. Hook Execution
-- Server logs show "OCSP HOOK CALLED" messages
-- Hook call counter increments correctly
-- Hook receives correct certificate chain and SNI information
-
-### 2. OCSP Delivery
-- OpenSSL client output contains "OCSP response:" section
